{"tid":1078231,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺唔食午餐，人都精神d ?","createTime":"2019-03-26T06:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T09:42:32.000Z","uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b7818c6f87df578df979116547e56e4d1956cae3","tid":1078231,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T06:59:37.000Z","msg":"其實你有食早餐就夠<br />\n午餐根本就唔重要<br />\n<br />\n食完午餐會令到你胰島素急升<br />\n令你胰島素嘅敏感度每況愈下<br />\n長久之下只會增加你患糖尿病嘅風險<br />\n再者，食完餐中午就會令你飯氣攻心<br />\n工作效率變得奇差<br />\n令到好多上班族靠餐後一杯咖啡或濃茶提神<br />\n好可惜咖啡因嘅提神功效鑒於耐受性既出現亦會逐漸變無效化<br />\n令到上班族好容易啡駁啡，咖啡因攝取嚴重超標<br />\n高濃度嘅咖啡因攝取對身體亦都係有害<br />\n唔好同我講咩食低GI既午餐就冇事呢d廢話<br />\n講就講得理想<br />\n你試吓隨意喺街既餐廳搵間低GI 嘅餐meun俾我？<br />\n根本成個香港市場都唔support 低GI 飲食 <br />\n呢個option根本係不切實際 <br />\n<br />\n呢個世界 no free lunch ？<br />\n我就話 <br />\n呢個世界 no need lunch"},{"pid":"1a79560d208236753a3eca97c20ffbaa79136c6e","tid":1078231,"uid":71092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多"},{"pid":"1c8097f608dd766d6f685b6ff4c863f3ca9c0e87","tid":1078231,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"屌又9up<br />\n之前明明話唔食早餐"},{"pid":"cb234e279021b031403176b247d511cbb99f7a9a","tid":1078231,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"咁我唔食早餐 將午餐變成早餐又點？"},{"pid":"cad9496adae7597aa59f85af1ef8b3c88ab6c370","tid":1078231,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:02:35.000Z","msg":"除非你自備低GI 既午餐飯盒/ 自己煮<br />\n否則唔食午餐就係你最好嘅選擇<br />\n但記住早餐要食多啲，營養要充足"},{"pid":"6d1f6eb2442952376a2554b72d319bef1851c7b1","tid":1078231,"uid":225760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ca347ac01a65c41b1689ee724e771481f45cefe","tid":1078231,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c8097f608dd766d6f685b6ff4c863f3ca9c0e87","tid":1078231,"uid":7915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:01:37.000Z","msg":"屌又9up<br />\n之前明明話唔食早餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:03:32.000Z","msg":"二選一 <br />\n唔食早餐就會變成18/6 間竭性斷食"},{"pid":"a91cd7b39540069b05e8a18f9a8f0e4190c3c40e","tid":1078231,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb234e279021b031403176b247d511cbb99f7a9a","tid":1078231,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"咁我唔食早餐 將午餐變成早餐又點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:04:05.000Z","msg":"咁就變成間竭性斷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab50985e14098ed8f1830849936a9f03cf9a462a","tid":1078231,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:04:37.000Z","msg":"9up王"},{"pid":"cbccfad759821d25f7990c55f9125617c6a7347e","tid":1078231,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2ac8ea464b749bf72ea5ac6c8fe40e0c31d16a0","tid":1078231,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T09:42:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}